<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lot-pron">lot <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /lɒt/    美 /lɑːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>大量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She gave the boys lots to eat. 
她给了男孩们很多吃的东西。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has invited nearly a hundred people but a lot aren’t able to come. 
他邀请了差不多100人，但很多人来不了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="a-lot-of-lots-of">a lot of / lots of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[接可数名词或不可数名词] 很多；许多：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She spends a lot of money on clothes. 
她花很多钱买衣服。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There were lots of people in the shop. 
商店里的人很多。</p></div></div>